headline: Is Raymond James Financial (RJF) Attractive After Strong Multi‑Year Share Price Gains?
summary: If you are wondering whether Raymond James Financial is currently priced attractively or stretched, the stock’s recent track record gives you plenty to think about. The share price sits at US$168.86, with returns of 3.9% over the last 7 days, 3.5% over the last 30 days, 3.2% year to date, 7.6% over 1 year, 59.0% over 3 years and 162.6% over 5 years. headline: What Catalysts Are Subtly Shifting The Narrative For Raymond James Financial (RJF)
summary: What the Small Shift in Fair Value Signals The latest update to the Raymond James Financial narrative comes with only a very small change in the modeled fair value, moving from about US$183.27 to roughly US$183.55, along with a slightly lower discount rate and marginally softer revenue growth assumptions.
